                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10181" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2565</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">319 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿智孪生，链动全球：数字生态元域下杭州中艺ESG实践之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Green Intelligence Twins, Chaining the World: Hangzhou Zhongyi’s ESG Practice Path in the Digital Ecology Meta-Domain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曹聪，张佳美，谷华杰，肖烨颖，方蕴雯，朱晨波</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杭州中艺实业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG数字化战略；数字孪生价值链；数智技术；可持续发展；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG Digitalization Strategy; Digital Twin Value Chain; Digital Intelligence Technology; Sustainability</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例剖析了杭州中艺实业股份有限公司（以下简称“杭州中艺”）在数智技术与可持续发展规则深度交织的新商业环境下，如何通过“技术链+价值链”双链协同机制重构ESG（环境、社会和公司治理，Environmental, Social and Governance）竞争力的创新实践。面对欧盟《企业可持续发展尽责指令》（Corporate Sustainability Due Diligence Directive）的跨境碳追溯合规要求及《2025年全球风险报告》揭示的供应链信息失真风险，杭州中艺以数智技术基座和可持续发展价值网络为核心驱动，通过引入IBM集成产品开发管理理念，成功研发全球首款智能阳光房产品。同步实施的“2+N”立体化升级模式不仅推动企业完成智慧化升级，更形成具有行业普适性的ESG数字化转型方法论。本案例为传统制造业破解合规成本与商业价值平衡难题提供实践样本，同时引发对数字时代企业可持续发展路径创新的理论思考，为全球产业链重构背景下的ESG战略升级提供决策参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study analyzes the innovative practices of Hangzhou Zhongyi Industrial Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as “Hangzhou Zhongyi”) in rebuilding ESG competitiveness through a dual-chain synergy mechanism of &quot;technology chain + value chain&quot; within a new business environment shaped by the deep integration of digital-intelligent technologies and sustainable development regulations. In response to the EU’s CSDDD cross-border carbon traceability compliance requirements and the supply chain distortion risks highlighted in the Global Risks Report 2025, Hangzhou Zhongyi, driven by a foundation of digital-intelligent technology and a sustainable value network, introduced IBM’s integrated product development management philosophy to successfully develop the world’s first intelligent sunroom product. The concurrently implemented “2+N” multi-dimensional upgrade model not only enabled the company to achieve intelligent transformation but also established a universally applicable ESG digital transformation methodology across the industry. This case provides a practical example for traditional manufacturing in balancing compliance costs with business value, while also prompting theoretical reflection on innovative sustainable development pathways for enterprises in the digital era, offering strategic insights for ESG upgrades under the global industrial chain restructuring context.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》、《责任与可续管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“技术链+价值链”双链驱动；理解动态能力如何协同支撑企业可持续创新路径；掌握动态能力理论在企业转型中的应用方法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
